      <div class="qa-body">
        <div class="qa-solution">
          <p>Filter the event log by <strong>process command line containing <code>del</code></strong>. This surfaces
            deletion commands executed by the attacker as part of their cleanup phase. Reviewing the log entries reveals
            a <code>del</code> command executed against files on a second machine — the hostname appears in the log
            source or command path, identifying it as the attacker's secondary target used to remove incriminating
            evidence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="report-img-block">
          <img src="images/Qradar/Deletion.png" alt="   " />
