      <div class="qa-body">
        <div class="qa-solution">
          <p>Filter for <strong>Event ID 4672</strong> (Special Privileges Assigned on Logon) combined with successful
            logon events. Event 4672 fires whenever a user with sensitive privileges (like Domain Admins membership)
            creates a new logon session. Reviewing the list of usernames associated with these events — excluding the
            built-in <code>administrator</code> account — reveals the second legitimate domain admin in the environment.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="report-img-block">
          <img src="images/Qradar/Event4672.png" alt="   " />
